# Title: BITS Transfer Job Download To Potential Suspicious Folder
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-28
# Level: high
# Description: Detects new BITS transfer job where the LocalName/Saved file is stored in a potentially suspicious location
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.persistence, attack.t1197
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/bits_client/win_bits_client_new_trasnfer_susp_local_folder.yml

EventID=16403 LocalName IN ("*\\Desktop\\*", "*C:\\Users\\Public\\*", "*C:\\PerfLogs\\*")